org.atlanmod.commons.io.serializer

Interface Serializer<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of (de)serialized objects
    U - the type of the basic representation of the objects
    All Superinterfaces:
    Converter<T,U>, Function<T,U>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BinarySerializer<T>, StringSerializer<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBinarySerializer, AbstractStringSerializer

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface Serializer<T,U>
extends Converter<T,U>
    An object that is responsible for encoding and decoding the basic representation of Objects.
